4 to complete 1 additional credit in English language arts,
5 mathematics, or science or 1 additional credit in a language other
6 than English, or requires the pupil to complete a formal career and
7 technical education program. This additional credit must be in
8 addition to the number of those credits otherwise required under
9 subsection (1) and section 1278a(1) or under section 1278a(2).
10 (k) If the parent or legal guardian of a pupil requests as
